      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">⚡</div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">EH Rated</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
        Insulation against electrical hazard exposure.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🦶</div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Puncture Resistant</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
        Protection against sharp objects penetrating the sole.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Article Grid -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Explore Topics</h2>
